153
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,930
What are you talking about?

154
00:14:29,930 --> 00:14:32,420
Do I need to refresh your memories?

155
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:36,030
When you initially ignored Ai Li Si, I could understand.

156
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:40,150
But that day she got watered down in the toilet, you both clearly saw it.

157
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,750
