00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:18,900
<i>Why were you injured that day?</i>

241
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:22,400
<i>Did you get into a fight with Chen Qi Tai?</i>

242
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,200
How did you know?

243
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:27,900
Because Chen Qi Tai also had wounds on his face.

244
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,700
<i>Yes.</i>

245
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,300
Was it because of me?

246
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:50,000
He Hao Yi, if I asked you to go bungee jumping with me again,

247
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:52,100
would you go?

248
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:58,200
<i>Would You?</i>

249
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:02,000
Would you jump with me?

250
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,200
Yes.

251
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,800
I would go.

252
00:25:17,230 --> 00:25:19,750
You really treat me well.

253
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:25,500
It turns out that I have so many good memories to remove.

254
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,600
<i>He Hao Yi,</i>

255
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:40,800
after I lost my memory, if you weren't able to convince Liu Xiao Fen,

256
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:43,600
I wouldn't be able to stay at your place.

257
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:51,300
<i>Whenever I lose the will to fight, you're the one to encourage me and cheer me on.</i>

258
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:57,400
If I were to write down all your good deeds on a piece of paper,

259
00:25:58,200 --> 00:26:00,900
can I fit everything on one A4-size paper?

260
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,800
Don't you have all kinds of notebooks?

261
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,400
That's true.

262
00:26:20,370 --> 00:26:21,990
Ai Li Si,

263
00:26:23,950 --> 00:26:26,990
<i>I know I may not have the right to say these words,</i>

264
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:32,000
<i>but let's forget about the bad things from the past.</i>

265
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:38,430
The reason that we reminisce about the past is to learn some lessons,

266
00:26:38,430 --> 00:26:41,230
and to not make the same mistake again.

267
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:45,600
<i>It wasn't easy for us to meet again.</i>

268
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:48,500
<i>It's not easy to meet for the second time.</i>

269
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:54,000
Let's not miss out on each other this time, okay?

270
00:26:54,000 --> 00:27:00,600
♫<i> I'm a little sad. Being around too many bright colors is very bitter. </i>♫

271
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:02,400
He Hao Yi,

272
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:10,800
you really are a good person, but I'm just not as positive as you are.

273
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:13,020
You've just forgotten that

274
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:18,200
I got all my good qualities from you.

275
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:29,400
♫<i> A transparent life is full of colors. </i>♫

276
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:33,800
♫<i> What's real? What's fake? Who cares that much? </i>♫

277
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:41,900
I will send a puzzle to you. If you can solve it, then we will meet there tomorrow.

278
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:46,400
Why do you have to go to so much trouble?

279
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:53,800
Didn't you say you want us to be like a couple

280
00:27:54,600 --> 00:28:00,100
who meets in a special place?

281
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:05,090
Okay, send it over.

282
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:09,400
♫<i> I'm a little sad. </i>♫

283
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:13,000
♫<i> Being around too many bright colors </i>♫

284
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:18,400
♫<i> is very bitter. </i>♫

285
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:22,400
♫<i> A simple life </i>♫

286
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:25,600
♫<i> is always wishing for simplicity and pure. </i>♫

287
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:31,500
The hint is just too obvious. It's not hard to guess at all.

288
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:39,700
Okay then. See you tomorrow. Good night.

289
00:28:45,810 --> 00:28:47,450
Good night.

290
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,800
See you tomorrow.

291
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:30,100
Oh, no. Did I guess wrong?

292
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,400
The lab journal.

293
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:27,200
<i>He Hao Yi,</i>

294
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:32,400
<i>when you see this letter, I will have already left.</i>

295
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:44,700
<i>The lab journal is something that both you and Capital wanted the most.</i>

296
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:48,800
<i>Just think of it as the last present from me to you.</i>

297
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:22,600
<i>After going on a date with you, I realized that although 13 years had passed,</i>

298
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:25,800
<i>you could still live well without me.</i>

299
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:30,100
<i>Without you, I also lived well.</i>

300
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:34,300
<i>We don't need to pretend that we still care about each other.</i>

301
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:42,300
<i>From now on, I don't want to see you. Don't look for me.</i>

302
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:48,500
<i>After you take this, we are squared.</i>

303
00:31:57,400 --> 00:32:03,400
<i>Thank you for letting me experience again the pure and happy feeling when I was 17.</i>

304
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:09,700
<i>He Hao Yi, goodbye.</i>

305
00:32:15,930 --> 00:32:17,960
Do you really want to do this?

306
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:24,200
I already gave the lab journal to He Hao Yi.

307
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:29,300
I don't want to do the research anymore.

308
00:32:30,130 --> 00:32:31,830
Why?

309
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:36,760
You've worked so hard on this research ever since your college days.

310
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:40,300
Are you really an impetuous person?

311
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:44,400
I originally thought not.

312
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:50,560
In the past, I was the "garbage-truck girl."

313
00:32:51,370 --> 00:32:54,990
I would take everything that nobody wanted.

314
00:32:54,990 --> 00:32:59,420
If there was anything someone wanted, I would find a way to give it to them.

315
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:06,100
That was a long time ago, so I thought I had changed.

316
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:11,960
But when I met He Hao Yi, it was still the same.

317
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:18,190
Because he wanted the lab journal so much, so I gave it to him.

318
00:33:20,350 --> 00:33:25,110
If you could give him that, then why can't you give him an opportunity?

319
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:32,200
These 13 years, I have watched over you.

320
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:36,000
You didn't cry or smile.

321
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:39,000
You were emotionless. You just suppressed yourself.

322
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:42,600
But after you met He Hao Yi, you started to smile.

323
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:46,600
He was the only one who could do this. And he is willing to do this for you now.

324
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:52,800
I really want to believe him,

325
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:59,740
but the one I can't believe is myself.

326
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:07,900
No matter what he does, I would be suspicious of him.

327
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:13,200
Whenever I see him, I worry about

328
00:34:13,200 --> 00:34:18,800
if they would all leave me because of my little mistake.

329
00:34:21,790 --> 00:34:24,220
So this time,

330
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:29,900
I want to be the first one to leave.

331
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:36,460
At the very least, he could get on the good side of me in my memories.

332
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,300
He Hao Yi is here.

333
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:49,000
You will help me, right?

334
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,500
You really...

335
00:34:54,990 --> 00:34:59,180
<i>Ai Li Si, are you really sure you want to do this?</i>

336
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:02,900
<i>I thought you really liked He Hao Yi.</i>

337
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:17,000
I also originally thought this.

338
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:21,100
That's why I did a small experiment.

339
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:23,800
What experiment?

340
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:29,060
I went on a date with him.

341
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:36,200
<i>Then I realized that...</i>

342
00:35:37,810 --> 00:35:42,280
I just wanted to fulfill the dream I had when I was 17.

343
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:47,210
That was to confess to him.

344
00:35:49,500 --> 00:35:52,100
<i>He really treats you well right now.</i>

345
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:56,100
<i>So what?</i>

346
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:05,000
When I was 27, they didn't show up to retrieve the time capsule.

347
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:10,400
I was sad, and I cried.

348
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:14,450
<i>Later, I pretended that nothing had happened.</i>

349
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:24,000
Right now, getting into a relationship

350
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:27,000
is a burden to me.

351
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,950
Then you still gave the lab journal to him?

352
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:39,100
<i>He wanted it, so I gave it to him. I can always start another research.</i>

353
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:44,600
If I keep the lab journal with me,

354
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:48,700
he would just keep pestering me.

355
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:54,100
But I don't want him to get close to me.

356
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,600
<i>It's annoying.</i>

357
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,900
He is really annoying!

358
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:13,000
He is annoying me to death!

359
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:17,600
♫<i> Where did the love between us fall off? </i>♫

360
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:22,600
♫<i> Even if this happiness we possess is just vain joy? </i>♫

361
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:28,570
♫<i> That shoulder you have leaned on is still here. </i>♫

362
00:37:28,570 --> 00:37:33,000
♫<i> I begrudge your breath. </i>

363
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:38,000
♫<i> Where does this never vanished love fall off? </i>♫

364
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:43,200
♫<i> I keep searching without caring at all. </i>♫

365
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:53,800
♫<i> Some people will let a person forget himself, but also remember himself. </i>♫

366
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:58,800
♫<i> I really want to love you. To persist until the end, </i>♫

367
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:03,300
♫<i> tell me how much courage it requires. </i>♫

368
00:38:09,810 --> 00:38:11,280
Are you back?

369
00:38:13,330 --> 00:38:15,180
What's up?

370
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:19,230
Didn't you go to look for Ai Li Si? Why do you have such an expression?

371
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:26,340
There will be no Ai Li Si from now on.

372
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:31,760
What do you mean?

373
00:38:48,080 --> 00:38:52,210
<i>He Hao Yi! Go on a date with me.</i>

374
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:54,990
<i>If I'm unreasonable to you today,</i>

375
00:38:54,990 --> 00:39:00,650
<i>just take it as a test for me to believe in you.</i>

376
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:05,120
<i>You'll always be here, right?</i>

377
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:10,820
<i>Even if I make you angry, you would still stay by my side. Am I right?</i>

378
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:15,120
<i>I just went on a date with him</i>

379
00:39:15,120 --> 00:39:19,580
<i>to fulfill the dream I had when I was 17.</i>

380
00:39:19,580 --> 00:39:21,930
<i>It's annoying.</i>

381
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:25,180
<i>He's really annoying!</i>

382
00:39:26,310 --> 00:39:28,980
<i>He is annoying me to death!</i>

383
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:43,450
Why did you call me?

384
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:49,380
To drink with me. It looks like you can't drink.

385
00:39:50,250 --> 00:39:52,890
I can't drink. If there is nothing, then I will go.

386
00:39:52,890 --> 00:39:54,240
Hey!

387
00:39:55,830 --> 00:39:58,080
Sit down.

388
00:39:58,750 --> 00:40:02,480
How could you know without trying? Come on, try it.

389
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:04,800
No need.

390
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:08,460
What's wrong? Now, I'm out of the game.

391
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:10,380
So even you just want to ignore me?

392
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:12,440
What do you mean?

393
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:15,710
I heard the conversation between you and Ai Li Si at her home.

394
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:19,120
You drank too much. Go home and rest.

395
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:22,500
Do I really look like I'm drunk, huh?!

396
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:25,170
Why should I keep my head clear?

397
00:40:26,230 --> 00:40:30,360
Even if I'm not sober, I don't know what Ai Li Si is thinking anyway. So why can't I get sober?

398
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:34,970
So many years have passed.

399
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:38,630
I thought Ai Li Si and I would have a chance to be together.

400
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:42,420
But in the end, it's just a one-sided wish from me.

401
00:40:42,420 --> 00:40:44,350
So are you giving up?

402
00:40:45,990 --> 00:40:50,480
Am I giving up? Good question. Let me ask myself.

403
00:40:56,450 --> 00:40:59,770
It's still pounding. Help me feel it.

404
00:40:59,770 --> 00:41:01,320
Stop it, okay?

405
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:03,890
- Stop it!<br>- Come on, just feel it.

406
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:06,440
It's still pounding.

407
00:41:07,010 --> 00:41:10,870
But my brain is dead.

408
00:41:12,190 --> 00:41:15,750
Do you know whose this is?

409
00:41:15,750 --> 00:41:18,870
Whose is it?

410
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:24,020
- I don't know.<br>- How can you not know?

411
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:28,290
You clearly know everything. You're the only one who knows everything! Huh?!

412
00:41:28,290 --> 00:41:30,330
Oh!

413
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:33,690
Something dropped.

414
00:41:33,690 --> 00:41:36,200
Oh, I picked up a heart. Is it yours?

415
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:40,860
Yeah, how did you know? Are you alone?

416
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:42,450
Do I look like two people?

417
00:41:42,450 --> 00:41:44,560
How humorous.

418
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:47,440
My name is Alice. What's your name?

419
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:50,260
- Alice? Like the Alice in "Alice in Wonderland"? <br>- Yes.

420
00:41:50,260 --> 00:41:52,690
Could it be such a coincidence?

421
00:41:52,690 --> 00:41:54,840
- Don't tell me you're called Alice, too?<br>- Yes, my name is also Alice.

422
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:57,020
You're also called Alice?!

423
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:01,350
Give me two glasses of wine. I'll treat these two Alices.

424
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:04,130
How great! He's treating us to drinks!

425
00:42:04,130 --> 00:42:07,650
- How many Alices are here? Raise your hands!<br> - Here... !

426
00:42:07,650 --> 00:42:10,270
I'll treat all Alices to drinks!

427
00:42:11,620 --> 00:42:15,390
Why are you treating us to drinks?

428
00:42:20,500 --> 00:42:24,200
- To Alice.<br> - Yeah. To Alice.

429
00:42:30,660 --> 00:42:34,540
Let me tell you. I also knew an Alice (Ai Li Si).

430
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,510
13 years ago.

431
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:38,550
13 years ago?

432
00:42:38,550 --> 00:42:40,730
What did the Alice from 13 years ago look like?

433
00:42:40,730 --> 00:42:42,660
<i>That's right. What did she look like?</i>

434
00:42:43,790 --> 00:42:47,280
Hey, Song Han Ming is over there. Let me take care of Ah Di myself.

435
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:50,580
Wait a minute. Let's take care of Ah Di first.

436
00:42:50,580 --> 00:42:53,150
<i>- It's this person.<br>- That's her.</i>

437
00:42:53,150 --> 00:42:55,770
Don't laugh anymore...

438
00:42:55,770 --> 00:42:59,760
- I always missed my chance with her.<br>- Missed your chance? How come?

439
00:43:01,010 --> 00:43:04,790
Only until today did I realize that...

440
00:43:04,790 --> 00:43:06,740
it's all my fault.

441
00:43:06,740 --> 00:43:08,840
How come? What happened?

442
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:11,130
It's just one mistake after another.

443
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:15,310
Okay, let's not talk about it anymore.

444
00:43:15,310 --> 00:43:17,080
None of you can leave.

445
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:19,770
<i>- Okay, none of us will leave. Let's talk about her more.</i><br>- She was on the track and field team.

446
00:43:19,770 --> 00:43:21,690
I could never catch up with her.

447
00:43:21,690 --> 00:43:25,740
- I kept chasing her, but now I have no more energy to chase. <br>- Let's not talk about her. Let's drink.

448
00:43:25,740 --> 00:43:28,310
I'm not going to chase her anymore...

449
00:43:28,310 --> 00:43:30,960
- He Hao Yi, it's enough. Don't drink anymore!<br>- Ah Di!

450
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:33,160
Let's go home... !

451
00:43:34,400 --> 00:43:38,230
Hey! Why are you two here? Let me introduce to you...

452
00:43:38,230 --> 00:43:44,810
Eh... Alice from Shilin, Alice from Tianmu, and Alice from Gaoxiong.

453
00:43:44,810 --> 00:43:47,150
Okay. Stop it.

454
00:43:47,150 --> 00:43:48,840
So many Alices.

455
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:51,180
You're drunk. How can there be so many Alices?

456
00:43:51,180 --> 00:43:53,630
Of the many Alices,

457
00:43:53,630 --> 00:43:56,600
which of them is my Ai Li Si?

458
00:43:57,510 --> 00:43:58,540
Where is Ai Li Si?

459
00:43:58,540 --> 00:44:01,860
Your Ai Li Si is at home. Let's go home, okay?

460
00:44:01,860 --> 00:44:03,490
Let's go home...

461
00:44:06,390 --> 00:44:07,740
Which one is my Ai Li Si?

462
00:44:07,740 --> 00:44:10,950
She's not here. Let's go.

463
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:16,870
- He Hao Yi!<br>- Hurry.

464
00:44:18,930 --> 00:44:20,640
You're so heavy.

465
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:26,090
Why did this rotten Ah Di drink so much? He's trying to tire me to death.

466
00:44:26,090 --> 00:44:28,610
Exactly!

467
00:44:28,610 --> 00:44:31,280
I've never seen him drink so much.

468
00:44:32,860 --> 00:44:36,660
He really never got drunk before. This is all because of her.

469
00:44:37,330 --> 00:44:39,310
Seriously.

470
00:44:44,660 --> 00:44:46,220
Ai Li Si...

471
00:44:53,470 --> 00:44:55,370
Let's go.

472
00:45:09,890 --> 00:45:12,870
Ah Di should be inside.

473
00:45:14,330 --> 00:45:17,630
You go.

474
00:45:17,630 --> 00:45:19,820
I don't want to.

475
00:45:19,820 --> 00:45:21,570
You're his sister!

476
00:45:21,570 --> 00:45:23,500
Just because I'm his sister, I can't say it.

477
00:45:23,500 --> 00:45:25,820
Why can't you say it?

478
00:45:25,820 --> 00:45:28,080
Then, what should we do?

479
00:45:38,350 --> 00:45:42,150
<i>It was all because of you. That's why Ai Li Si hasn't come home yet.</i>

480
00:45:42,150 --> 00:45:46,060
<i>What are you talking about? It's because you lack persuasion skills, okay?</i>

481
00:45:46,060 --> 00:45:49,600
<i>Who was the one that got upset and said, "Let's go. Let's go," and then left?</i>

